Global DDR5 Temperature Sensor (TS) Market Insights
DDR5 Temperature Sensor (TS) Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 14.5% from 2024 to 2030.

DDR5 Temperature Sensor (TS) Market Overview
The DDR5 Temperature Sensor (TS) market has seen significant growth due to the increasing demand for high-performance memory modules in computing, gaming, and AI systems. The global market size for DDR5 Temperature Sensors was valued at approximately USD 400 million in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 20% from 2025 to 2030. This growth can be attributed to the rising need for efficient thermal management in advanced DRAM modules, which play a crucial role in optimizing system performance and longevity. Additionally, with the increasing adoption of DDR5 memory technology in data centers and gaming systems, the demand for temperature sensors tailored for DDR5 modules is on the rise.

